:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(632,106,'_edit_last','1'),(633,106,'_edit_lock','1484834151:1'),(634,106,'itinerary','<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Day 1 :</strong> On Arrival you will be greeted and assisted by our official at Bagdogra Airport(IXB) / New Jalpaiguri Railway Station (NJP) – He will assist you for the forwarding journey to Lataguri (100 Kilometers, 2½ - 3 hours) via Sevoke Kalimandir, Coronation Bridge - Lunch on the way in Dhaba / Resort. After lunch Visit Gorumara National Park for Jungle Safari or Any one Point. Night stay at Lataguri / Murti / Dhupjhora.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Day 2 :</strong> Early Morning visit Gorumara National Park / Chapramari W.L.S. any one point. After lunch visit Gorumara National Park / Chapramari W.L.S. any one point. Night stay at Lataguri / Murti / Dhupjhora</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Day 3 :</strong> Fullday Sightseeing Samsing, Suntalekhola, Rocky Island, Jhalong, Bindu. After breakfast start for full day visit at Samsing, Suntalekhola, Rocky Island, Jhalong and Bindu. Night stay at Suntalekhola / Jhalong / Lataguri.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Day 4 :</strong> Proceed for Jaldapara via South khayerbari. After breakfast proceed for Jaldapara National Park. After lunch visit South khayerbari. Night stay at Madarihat. (Jaldapara)</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Day 5 :</strong> Jaldapara &amp; Chilapata Safari. Early morning visit to Jaldapara National Park. Proceed to Chilapata Forest and visit Nolrajar Gorh. Night stay at Chilapata / Jaldapara.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Day 6 :</strong> Visit Buxa Tiger Reserve, Jayanti and Pukri Lake. After breakfast start journey for Buxa Tiger Reserve. After lunch visit Jayanti and Pukri Lake. Night stay at Jaldapara / Lataguri.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Day 7 :</strong> Departure. Early morning breakfast - then drive to Siliguri, on the way to Bagdogra Airport (IXB) / New Jalpaiguri Railway Station (NJP)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(635,106,'_itinerary','field_58785fe0c4e9f'),(636,106,'cost_per_adult','9750'),(637,106,'_cost_per_adult','field_58786011c4ea0'),(638,106,'places_covered','Gorumara, Chapramari, Chilapata, Jaldapara, Murti, Jhalong, Bindu, Samsing, Suntalekhola, South Khaerbari, Jayanti, Buxa Tiger Reserve'),(639,106,'_places_covered','field_5878603bc4ea1'),(640,106,'package_includes','<ul>\r\n 	<li>6 Nights accommodation in above mentioned hotel / resort in base category room</li>\r\n 	<li>Transfer in Exclusive Air-Conditioned cars</li>\r\n 	<li>Sightseeing as per itinerary</li>\r\n 	<li>Food as per complementary breakfast and Lunch / Dinner</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplementary Cost - (Additional 2500 for Cake + Decoration + Candle light dinner)\r\nTribal Dance Show &amp; BBQ (on request &amp; subject to extra cost</li>\r\n</ul>'),(641,106,'_package_includes','field_5878606dc4ea2'),(642,106,'package_excludes','<div>\r\n<ul class=\"download\">\r\n 	<li>Air Fare / Train Fare</li>\r\n 	<li>All meals other than those specified in ‘Cost Includes’</li>\r\n 	<li>Expenses of personal nature</li>\r\n 	<li>Any other items not mentioned in ‘Cost Includes’</li>\r\n 	<li>Entrance fees</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),(643,106,'_package_excludes','field_587860fac4ea3'),(644,106,'booking_procedure','<div>\r\n<ul class=\"download\">\r\n 	<li>Just pay 25 % of the package cost inclusive of taxes and full amount of the airlines cost. You will get a booking confirmation voucher within 240 minutes of the payment receipt and your booking status will be \"<b>BOOKING HOLD- CONFIRMED</b>\"</li>\r\n 	<li>Please do not forget to send one email to <em>enq@dream-destinations.com</em> marking a copy to <em>accounts@dream-destinations.com</em>\r\npost payment mentioning your reference number. If you do not get voucher on-time you may call us at toll free: 18001203900 / +91-9831933166</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),(645,106,'_booking_procedure','field_58786115c4ea4'),(64